# New-card compat (wave 3): Healing Salve — scripted ACTIVE instant (Charm).
#
# Healing Salve is a {W} instant "Choose one —":
#   A:SP$ Charm | Choices$ DBGainLife,DBPreventDmg
#     DBGainLife : DB$ GainLife | ValidTgts$ Player | LifeAmount$ 3
#     DBPreventDmg: DB$ PreventDamage | ValidTgts$ Any | Amount$ 3
# (CR 601 casting, CR 700.2 modal "choose one", CR 119 life gain.)
#
# Tracking issue: Card Compatibility: Healing Salve.
#
# Aspects exercised:
#   1. Parses + castable as a {W} instant (spell cast assertion).
#   2. Modal Charm: the engine offers the two modes and the gain-life mode is
#      chosen (P0 is below starting life and there is no incoming damage to
#      prevent, so gain-life is the live, deterministic pick).
#   3. The gain-life mode adds exactly 3 life to the targeted player (CR 119.3).
#
# Scenario:
#   - P0 at 15 life with Healing Salve in hand and a Plains to pay {W}.
#   - Script: P0 casts Healing Salve targeting itself; gains 3 life -> 18.
#
# HOW TO RUN / VERIFY interactively:
#   mtg tui --start-state test_puzzles/newcard_healing_salve_gain_life.pzl \
#       --p1 heuristic --p2 heuristic --seed 42 -v 2 --no-color-logs
# The log shows "chooses mode: Target player gains 3 life." and P0 15 -> 18.

[metadata]
Name:New Card - Healing Salve Gains 3 Life
Goal:Win
Turns:1
Difficulty:Easy
Description:P0 at 15 life casts Healing Salve ({W} modal instant), choosing the gain-life mode targeting itself, ending at 18. Backs Card Compatibility: Healing Salve (SP$ Charm with DBGainLife / DBPreventDmg; CR 700.2 modal, CR 119 life gain).

[state]
turn=1
activeplayer=p0
activephase=MAIN1
p0life=15
p0hand=Healing Salve
p0battlefield=Plains
p0library=Plains;Plains;Plains;Plains;Plains

p1life=20
p1battlefield=
p1library=Mountain;Mountain;Mountain;Mountain;Mountain

[p0_script]
# Cast Healing Salve at self; the engine takes the gain-life mode (the only
# live mode here — there is no incoming damage to prevent).
cast Healing Salve targeting p0

[assertions]
# The modal instant was actually cast by the script.
spell cast Healing Salve
# P0 gained at least 3 life via the gain-life mode (event-log delta).
life gained ge 3
# Final life is exactly 15 + 3 = 18 (deterministic single-turn puzzle).
life eq 18
